flowchart-diagram





title ITSM Chatbot Data Flow
direction right

// Groups and nodes
User Interaction [color: blue, icon: user] {
  User [shape: oval, color: lightblue, icon: user]
  Web App [color: blue, icon: monitor]
}

AI Processing [color: purple, icon: gcp-ai-platform] {
  Azure OpenAI [color: purple, icon: azure-openai]
  Determine intent [shape: diamond, color: purple, icon: help-circle]
}

External Integrations [color: teal, icon: layers] {
  SharePoint [color: teal, icon: azure-sharepoint]
  ServiceNow [color: teal, icon: ourlogo]
}

User Response [color: blue, icon: message-square] {
  Web App Response [color: blue, icon: monitor]
  User Receives Response [shape: oval, color: lightblue, icon: user]
}

// Relationships
User > Web App: Submit query
Web App > Azure OpenAI: Send user query
Azure OpenAI > Determine intent

Determine intent > SharePoint: Informational query
Determine intent > ServiceNow: Service/ticket query

SharePoint > Web App Response: Return knowledge article
ServiceNow > Web App Response: Return ticket status or confirmation

Web App Response > User Receives Response: Display response

// Loop for further queries
User < User Receives Response: New query (optional)





